  kernel 2.6.

*dosemu-1.1.99.1 (01 Oct 2003)

  01 Oct 2003; Hanno Boeck <hanno@gentoo.org> dosemu-1.1.99.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Cleaned up ebuild a lot, strip -O3 and above to -O2.

*dosemu-1.1.5-r1 (20 Jun 2003)

