*dosemu-1.1.3-r1 (27 Jul 2002)

  19 Oct 2002; Daniel Ahlberg <aliz@gentoo.org> dosemu-1.1.3-r1.ebuild :
  Updated to mirror://sourceforge in SRC_URI.

